{"id": 1179, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，怎样看电影让你更像一个中产阶级？", "description": "人是铁，范儿是钢，一天不装憋得慌。对于中产阶级这个可爱的群体，我们充满了爱意。好奇心研究所会不定期推出紧跟时代节奏的“中产阶级装腔指南”，和大家一起分享研究生活的心得。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 7141, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160824180945zJ3gQ7hNYdjZC14s.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-05T17:00:05Z", "questions": [{"id": 1064, "title": "现如今，怎样看电影让你更像一个中产阶级？", "content": "如何看电影让你更像中产阶级？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 109847, "content": "一年里面看电影最多的时候是电影节的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20160822181907TxEpDy97HsgNSnjq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 109848, "content": "崇古，大量收藏默片黑白片", "image": "img/option/option/20160822181928d1P2e5Aq0SkH4GVo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 109849, "content": "会买一个投影仪在家里看收藏的蓝光碟", "image": "img/option/option/201608221819534u5R103rfD8SgJQO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 109851, "content": "相比大片，更愿意谈论小众片子", "image": "img/option/option/20160822182027MCxluVpkHhqO2abZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 109852, "content": "看电影评分不上豆瓣", "image": "img/option/option/20160822182054dusp0LGrzgZwKSjT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 109853, "content": "在所有电影tag里面“冷门高分“最吸引他们", "image": "img/option/option/20160822182119qES0rZiKLesxHwDm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 109854, "content": "种草电影里的一些小众配饰/家具", "image": "img/option/option/20160822182135GaR4nF6YPjbp9T3i.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}